Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:10.22,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:14.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,全部終わってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,告白のために頑張ったもんな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:22.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ヤバい　死にたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:26.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あの夜麦は来なかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:31.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,結局あの後　次の日の夕方になって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦から来たのはこの一言だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ムッカつく　ホントあり得ない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:45.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,告白　もしかしてうまくいった？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,バカじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:50.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,騙されてるに決まってんじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:55.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,バカね　たぶらかされたいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:57.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,男はみーんな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:05.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,嘘　ホントに涼しい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,軽井沢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:57.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,失恋旅行？　傷心旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それも一気に２人分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:04.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いやいや　片方とはまだ始まってもなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,さすが避暑地だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,風が気持ちぃー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:13.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何かこの霧と地形のおかげらしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいじゃん　別に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:24.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私たちのこと誰も知ってる人いない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,二人きりなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:31.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃんって　こういうとき結構強引なんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そんな顔　ずるいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,正直
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何かしている方が気が紛れた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:48.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私　失恋したんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:55.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火　来てくれて　ありがとね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:04:01.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,っていうか　すごいね　軽井沢に別荘持ってるって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:06.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いや　うちじゃないよ　親戚んちの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,古いから　あんま期待しないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すごい　すてき
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:13.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:18.12,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,他に誰もいないから　今日から二人きりだね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,さあ　ようこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.61,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いらっしゃいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,空気おもーっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おいしいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:45.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,味はもうホント
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:49.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗もおいしい？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.78,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おいしいわよ　そりゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,篤也が作ったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃんのいとこ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,横顔似てる…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:08.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火　先お風呂入っちゃっていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:11.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいの　洗い物…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいのいいの　疲れたでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　お先に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:25.72,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,気持ちいい…んだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ちょっと恥ずかしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,眺めはいいんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ちょっと　近い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:39.10,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そう？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ここ意外とキッチン狭いよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,怒ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,当たり前でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どのくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:48.72,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,察して
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,怒ってても早苗は綺麗だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:54.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,さっさと洗って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺着替え持ってきてない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,知らない　嫌なら離れて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:12.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:14.72,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,びちゃびちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:15.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,知らないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何か盛り上がってる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:18.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,本当に許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:24.32,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そもそも何で旅行のこと知ってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.78,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗んちに電話した
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,せっかく二人っきりだったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.66,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,チャンスだったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:34.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火が失恋して　あいつとも別れて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:38.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,この旅行で物にするつもりだった？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そうよ　それをあんたが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,違うでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ホントはあの子が早苗を好きになるはずないって分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:52.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,最後に思い出…欲しかっただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,うるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗の方が声大きいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:02.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,綺麗に終わりたいって　そんなに思っちゃいけないの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:05.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,綺麗に終わらせてあげたかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:09.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗はそこまで強くない…と俺は思う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,うるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.12,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今日はもう絶対部屋に入ってこないで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから声…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:28.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どうして　何が駄目なの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,他人に私の何が分かるの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:35.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,体熱い　花火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:38.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お…お風呂入ったから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いい匂いがする
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ずっと誰にも見せなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:49.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,知ってほしいとも思わなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今日するの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:54.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,するよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だ…だ…だって二人っきりじゃな…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,隣の部屋にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,声　抑えてね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:09.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,触れてなお　恋をしてなお
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私は孤独を選んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:18.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,終わりくらい自分で決めて　何が悪いの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:26.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何か目覚めちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:31.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,手帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:40.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:46.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,軽井沢行きの　新幹線の切符だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もしかして…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まだ震えてるね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そうだ　こんなのしかないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:08.40,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,誰かが触れれば　壊れてしまうほど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:12.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もろく　弱ってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:19.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それでも心は　ずっと息をしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:31.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早起き
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そっちも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:42.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,散歩します？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,湖なんて　普段見ない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:04.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あんたさ　誰のことが好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:08.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,い…いきなり何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.84,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいから答えて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:15.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そ…そんなの　い…今は分からないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もっと分かりやすく言った方がよかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:23.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗に対する気持ちだけ決めて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,他はどうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:29.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗は誰かの代わりにしていい人じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,絶対にこの旅行中に決めて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:45.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私はもう分かってるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:54.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すっごい　テンション上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:56.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん　服好きだもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,買った買ったー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:09.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,大満足だね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:12.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,夏休み短期バイト分つぎ込んだわ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:17.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,こんなに楽しそうなえっちゃん　久しぶりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,木陰落ち着くね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:22.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:22.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう　変なとこ投げないでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ごめんごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:43.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗は誰かの代わりにしていい人じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:47.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そんなの…分かってるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,この気持ちは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お願い　今だけは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:09.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,誰もこの感情に名前なんて付けないで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:13.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,最後に…するから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいところで声掛けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何でそんな古いのやってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.74,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ここレトロゲーしかないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やだ　風邪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おかえり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なに　大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,平気
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.78,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,寝てくる　うつすから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:47.22,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,絶対にこの旅行中に決めて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:56.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,また死んだ　もうやだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何回目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:59.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん　よわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火意外とうまい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:05.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私は小さい頃よくお兄ちゃんちでやってた…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いや　もう大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:11.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ホントに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:19.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火がずっと好きだったの　鐘井先生だったんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,完全に振られちゃったけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:26.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,むしろ　ホント今はすっきり…っていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:31.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ヤバい　ちょっと今泣いてる場合じゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:34.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火はよく頑張ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,真っすぐぶつかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:43.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私が何をしたってやっぱり　あなたは染まらなかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん　私…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:48.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃんにも言わなきゃいけないことが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:54.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今度は私が答えを出さなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今まで付き合わせてごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火優しいから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:09.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今まで散々付き合わせてごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,わがまま聞いてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,違う違う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,楽しかったし　うれしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:21.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だからもう…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,これ以上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:24.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,違うの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,つけ込んだのは私　わがままなのは私
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,全部私なの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もういいよ　花火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私　あなたを諦めるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,旅行の前から決めてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火がきちんと失恋して
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:46.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それでも　私のことそういうふうに見なかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:50.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そのときは　花火から離れようって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どうして…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:58.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,つらいもの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:03.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,寝室分けてあるから　朝は別で帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:04.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おやすみ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:07.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん　私　ちっとも優しくなんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:21.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,聞いて　私も言おうと思ってたことがあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私と友達でいて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ふざけないで　いいかげんにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:32.61,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どれだけ残酷なこと言ってるか分かってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:36.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いまさら友達面してなんて　できるわけないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:40.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私がどれだけ…どれだけ好きだったかなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:42.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,知らないくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:48.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,雨が降ってた　あの日も…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あの日の私の弱さが　過ちが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あなたをこんなに苦しめた　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.74,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なら今度は絶対諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:05.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃんは心の中を誰にも知られなくていいと言った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:08.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そんなの…独りぼっちと変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:13.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今までの関係を続けても　ここで関係を終わらせても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:16.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃんの扉は閉ざされたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから一人でいいんだってば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.84,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ほっといてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう入ってこないで…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,や…やだ　もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:28.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私が…私が知りたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:33.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,これからあなたのことは私が知りたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:36.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,教えてほしいの　何だって…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そう　なれるまで待つから…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:43.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,本当の私なんて　きっとろくでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あなたはきっと嫌いになる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そしたらどうやって立ち直ればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いつまででも　待つから…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:55.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,怖いのに　すごくすごく怖いのに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:59.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どうして　一人じゃ生きられないんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あのね　やっと気付いたの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:09.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あなたも私と同じおびえた目をしてること
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:12.84,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:15.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いつになるか分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:21.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まだすごく好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でも　頑張るから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,頑張って　忘れるから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:39.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,忘れなきゃいけないのに　忘れたくない味がした
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう帰っちゃったの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そうだよ　始発で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:55.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何だ　全然話せなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:59.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいから　病人はおとなしくしてなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:01.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗　頑張ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,うるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,病人はさっさと熱下げて帰るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:09.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗には俺がいるじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:17.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あんたもだし　少しは信じてみようかな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:23.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,未来のことなんて　まだ何も分からないから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから信じる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:30.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それは　お守りみたいにささやかで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:32.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,心に灯ると温かい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:43.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,久しぶりの校舎　教室　話し声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:48.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どことなく居心地が悪いのは　心細いのは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,新学期だからじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:57.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,仕方ないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:01.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まだ痛む　まだ染みる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,仕方ないの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,鴎端さんがパンをむさぼり食ってるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.58,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すごい絵だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:15.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おなかすいてたのかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:18.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おいしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何よ　暗ーい顔して
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あら　一人で下校？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:29.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そうだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もしかしてあんたも振られたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.12,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,「も」って何よ「も」って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あんたはもともと振られっぱなしでしょうが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ホントムカつくやつね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:43.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どっちがよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何なの　何が言いたいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:51.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私の方がずっと長く　真っすぐに麦を好きだったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だからすっきりしてんの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:02.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,自力でゲットした購買のデニッシュもおいしいってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あんたも自分だけで歩いてみたら分かるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:11.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,この世界で　たった一人きりになった気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ただ立ち尽くしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どうしてだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:20.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,一人で歩きだすことなんて　考えもしなかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.38,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おかしいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:30.38,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,家庭訪問ってやつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.61,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ちょっと憧れてたの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:36.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,保護者に挨拶して　お茶出されて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やめてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,先生ぶるの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:45.61,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やめないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:49.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だって　本当に先生なんだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だ…だけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:51.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だけど？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,嘘じゃないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ほら　言って　「先生」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:03.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ホントよ　今日は真面目に家庭訪問しただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:06.22,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,せ…先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:11.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そしたらね　保護者不在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:15.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,相手は男の子で　二人きりで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,仕方ないよね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,----------TEXT_CN----------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.25,0:00:10.22,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小繪
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.60,0:00:14.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,全都做完了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,為了表白我也是拼了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.29,0:00:22.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,完了 好想死
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.30,0:00:26.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那天晚上麥沒來
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.81,0:00:31.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,結果 到了第二天傍晚
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,他只發來這麼一句話
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,氣死我了 太不像話了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.57,0:00:45.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,難道他表白成功了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.70,0:00:50.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,他肯定被她給騙了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.85,0:00:55.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳才笨 他巴不得被我騙呢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.97,0:00:57.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,男人都這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.70,0:01:05.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,去
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,天啊 真的好涼快
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,輕井澤
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.60,0:02:57.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這是失戀之旅 還是傷心之旅？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,居然同時失戀兩次
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.82,0:03:04.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不對 我和其中一個還什麼都不算呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不愧是避暑勝地啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,風都格外涼爽
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.01,0:03:13.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,據說是因為這裡的霧和地形
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小繪…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.08,0:03:24.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這地方又沒人認識我們
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,只有我們倆
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.30,0:03:31.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小繪在這種時候可真夠霸道的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,笑容還這麼無害
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,其實
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,找點事做還能轉移注意力
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.90,0:03:48.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,畢竟我失戀了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.93,0:03:55.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,花火 謝謝妳陪我來
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.45,0:04:01.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,話說回來 妳家真厲害 居然在輕井澤有別墅
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.18,0:04:06.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不 不是我家的 是我親戚家的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,很老舊了 所以別太期待哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好氣派 好漂亮
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.82,0:04:13.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喜歡就好
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.44,0:04:18.12,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這裡沒有其他人 從今天開始就我們倆哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,來 請進吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.61,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,氣氛好僵
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.49,0:04:45.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,味道好極了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.04,0:04:49.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早苗 好吃嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.78,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,當然好吃了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你做的能不好吃嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小繪的表親
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,他們的側臉好像…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.54,0:05:08.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,花火 妳可以先去泡澡了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.13,0:05:11.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不太好吧 碗筷還沒洗…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,沒關係 妳都累壞了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那我先去了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.36,0:05:25.72,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,舒服…倒是舒服
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,就是有點難為情啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,風景還是很美的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,靠太近了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.38,0:05:39.10,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,有嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,沒想到這裡的廚房這麼小
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,廢話
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,有多生氣
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.78,0:05:48.72,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,自己看
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳生氣的樣子也很漂亮
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.80,0:05:54.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,快點洗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我沒帶換洗的衣服來
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,管你呢 怕弄髒就離遠點
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.49,0:06:12.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,宰了你
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.69,0:06:14.72,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都濕透了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.72,0:06:15.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,關我什麼事
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,他們鬧得很歡啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.78,0:06:18.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我和你沒完
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.14,0:06:24.32,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,話說你怎麼知道我來旅行的事
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.78,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我往妳家打電話了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好不容易只有我和她
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.66,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,多難得的機會啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.04,0:06:34.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,花火失戀了 又和那傢伙分手了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.85,0:06:38.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳想藉這次旅行得到她嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是啊 結果被你搞砸了…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,胡說
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,其實妳早就知道她是不可能喜歡上妳的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.42,0:06:52.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳只是想…留下最後的回憶
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳似乎比我更吵
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.62,0:07:02.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我只想好聚好散而已 這也不行嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.32,0:07:05.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,雖然我也想讓妳好聚好散
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.21,0:07:09.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,但我覺得…妳並沒有那麼堅強
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.12,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,今天你絕對不許進我們房間
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,別大聲喊…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.06,0:07:28.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,憑什麼管我 我哪裡做錯了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,旁人對我又了解多少
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.81,0:07:35.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,花火 妳身上好熱
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.21,0:07:38.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,因…因為我泡過澡了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,香香的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我從未以真心示人
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.01,0:07:49.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,也不打算讓任何人知曉
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,今天要做嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.82,0:07:54.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,但…但…但是今天還有別人…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,他就在隔壁房間
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小點聲哦
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.05,0:08:09.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,靠近以後 痴戀以後
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我仍選擇了孤獨
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.33,0:08:18.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,自己的結局 還不能由自己來決定嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.80,0:08:26.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,睡不著了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.88,0:08:31.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,花火…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,記事本…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.89,0:08:40.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是小繪的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.57,0:08:46.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,去輕井澤的新幹線車票
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這難道是…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳還在發抖啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這個給妳 不嫌棄就收下吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.16,0:09:08.40,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我卸下防備 整個人脆弱到
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.29,0:09:12.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,彷彿一碰就會崩潰
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.49,0:09:19.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,但曾經 至少我的心還活著
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.66,0:09:31.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,起得真早
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳也是
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.26,0:09:42.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,去散步嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,平常很少見到湖泊啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.52,0:10:04.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,問妳個問題 妳到底喜歡誰
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.38,0:10:08.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼這麼突然
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.84,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,快回答我
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.12,0:10:15.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這…這個嘛 我…我現在還不清楚
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,看來我應該問得更直白一點
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.84,0:10:23.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,趕快看清對早苗的感情吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,其他的都無所謂
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.05,0:10:29.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早苗她不該被妳拿來做別人的替身
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳務必在這次旅行中做個了斷
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.81,0:10:45.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,他說的我早就知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.52,0:10:54.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,太棒了 我好興奮
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.54,0:10:56.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你就喜歡各種衣服嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,大買特買
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.92,0:11:09.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好滿足啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.53,0:11:12.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我把暑假做短工賺的錢都花光了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.80,0:11:17.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好久沒見小繪笑得這麼開心了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,樹蔭下好舒服
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.00,0:11:22.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.41,0:11:22.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真是的 別亂扔啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.49,0:11:43.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早苗她不該被妳拿來做別人的替身
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.96,0:11:47.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我早就知道…不該這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這份感情是…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,拜託了 此時此刻…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.84,0:12:09.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,誰都不要給這份感情下定義
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.81,0:12:13.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我會…做個了斷的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳非在關鍵時刻喊我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎麼玩這麼老的遊戲
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.74,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這裡只有老遊戲
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不是感冒了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.78,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我去睡了 免得傳染給你們
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.97,0:12:47.22,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳務必在這次旅行中做個了斷
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.36,0:12:56.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我又死了 不玩了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都第幾次了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.82,0:12:59.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小繪 妳好弱
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,想不到妳這麼強
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.28,0:13:05.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我小時候經常在哥哥家玩這個來著…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,沒事 我已經放下了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.76,0:13:11.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.81,0:13:19.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳喜歡的人一直都是鍾井老師吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,可惜我徹底被拒了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.57,0:13:26.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不過 現在我反而覺得…很輕鬆
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.28,0:13:31.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,糟了 現在可不能哭…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.48,0:13:34.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳已經盡力了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,坦白了自己的心意
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.86,0:13:43.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,看來無論我做什麼 都無法影響到妳
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小繪 我…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.48,0:13:48.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我有些話一定要對妳說
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.82,0:13:54.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這次該我給出答案了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉 讓妳陪了我這麼久
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳太善良了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.48,0:14:09.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉 總讓妳陪我胡鬧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳肯包容我的任性
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不對不對
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我真的很高興 很快樂
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.49,0:14:21.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以我們…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,到此為止吧…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.56,0:14:24.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,耍賴的人是我 任性的人是我
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都是我
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不必再說了 花火
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我要放棄妳了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我在旅行前就決定好了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,如果妳失戀之後
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.61,0:14:46.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,還是對我沒有那種意思的話
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.45,0:14:50.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我就離開妳身邊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.09,0:14:58.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這樣太痛苦了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.76,0:15:03.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我去別的房間睡 明早分頭離開吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.64,0:15:04.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.49,0:15:07.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小繪…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小繪 我一點都不善良
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小繪
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.08,0:15:21.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,聽我說 我也有話放在心裡很久了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小繪
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,請繼續和我做朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了 妳鬧夠了沒有
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.04,0:15:32.61,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳懂不懂自己說的話有多殘忍
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.96,0:15:36.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,事到如今我怎麼可能若無其事地和妳做朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.90,0:15:40.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳根本…根本就不知道我有多麼
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.16,0:15:42.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,多麼喜歡妳
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.41,0:15:48.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那天也下著雨…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那天我的軟弱和過失
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,竟讓妳如此痛苦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.74,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那麼這次我絕不放棄
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.53,0:16:05.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小繪 妳說過不必讓別人知曉自己的真心
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.34,0:16:08.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,但那只是…變相的孤獨
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.20,0:16:13.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,無論我們繼續在一起 還是從此一刀兩斷
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.45,0:16:16.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳的內心都依然緊鎖著
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以說 我一個人待著就好
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.84,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,少來管我
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,別再闖進我的心…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不…不要 夠了…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.76,0:16:28.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我想…我想去了解
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.88,0:16:33.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,從今以後 我想更多地了解妳
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.50,0:16:36.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,什麼都可以 我只希望妳能告訴我…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我會等到妳願意開口的那一天…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.97,0:16:43.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真實的我 肯定一無是處
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,肯定會惹妳厭煩
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,到那時我該怎麼振作起來
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我會一直等下去…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.09,0:16:55.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我真的很怕 怕得不得了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.01,0:16:59.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,為什麼人就是無法自生自滅呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,直到現在 我才發現
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.65,0:17:09.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳和我一樣 眼中也充滿恐懼
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.93,0:17:12.84,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.00,0:17:15.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道要等到什麼時候
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.13,0:17:21.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,因為我還是好喜歡妳
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,但是 我會努力的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我會努力忘記妳的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.48,0:17:39.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,明知道要忘記 卻難以忘記
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,她這就回去了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是啊 坐首班車
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.28,0:17:55.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣 我都沒跟她說上話
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.41,0:17:59.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,別折騰了 病號就老老實實地躺著
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.46,0:18:01.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早苗 妳好拼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你好煩
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,病號就趕緊給我退燒走人
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.04,0:18:09.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳不是還有我嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,也對啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.74,0:18:17.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你也和我差不多 我就信你一次吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.69,0:18:23.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,未來的事情 目前都還是未知數
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以我才相信未來
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.32,0:18:30.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這小小的信念就像護身符一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.56,0:18:32.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,放在心中十分溫暖
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.85,0:18:43.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,久違的教學樓 教室 喧鬧聲
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.17,0:18:48.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,總覺得有點難受 有點不安
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,並不是因為新學期
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.97,0:18:57.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這樣也是無可奈何
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.48,0:19:01.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,還會心痛 還會心酸
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,也只好這樣了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,鷗端同學正在狂啃麵包
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.58,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那畫面太美…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.93,0:19:15.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,估計是餓壞了吧…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.93,0:19:18.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,搞定
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎麼愁眉苦臉的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,哎呀 一個人回家嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.22,0:19:29.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是又怎樣
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,難不成妳也被甩了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.12,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,加個「也」是什麼意思
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,人家從一開始就沒正眼瞧過妳吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳簡直討厭死了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.42,0:19:43.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,到底誰討厭啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 妳到底想說什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.97,0:19:51.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我對麥的喜歡 可比妳長久得多 真誠得多
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以我現在一身輕鬆
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.18,0:20:02.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,自己去小賣店買的起酥麵包 吃起來也很香
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妳也試著自己走一走就明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.62,0:20:11.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這些年來 我覺得自己被全世界遺棄
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,只是傻傻地站在原地
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.17,0:20:20.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我從來沒有想過 要自己向前走呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.38,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.46,0:20:30.38,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的家訪啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.61,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我之前還很期待呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.49,0:20:36.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,向家長問好 等家長給我上茶
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,別裝老師了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.46,0:20:45.61,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我才不要
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.82,0:20:49.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,因為 我本來就是老師
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.06,0:20:51.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,可是什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我沒有說謊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,叫聲「老師」來聽聽
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.93,0:21:03.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是真的 我今天是誠心來做家訪的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.17,0:21:06.22,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,老…老師…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.17,0:21:11.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,結果呢 家長不在
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.44,0:21:15.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,只剩下孤男寡女 共處一室
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,這樣也是無可奈何
